{"word":"G4135 - πληροφορέω - plērophoréō - play-rof-or-eh'-o - Most surely believe","slug":"G4135","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πληροφορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>plērophoréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>play-rof-or-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Most surely believe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C6;&#x03BF;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - ple&#x0304;rophoreo&#x0304;</b> - <i>play-rof-or-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4134\">G4134</a> and <a href=\"#/G5409\">G5409</a>; to <i>carry</i> out <i>fully</i> (in evidence), that is, <i>completely assure</i> (or <i>convince</i>), <i>entirely accomplish:</i> - most surely believe, fully know (persuade), make full proof of."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1603\">G1603</a>, <a href=\"#/G1604\">G1604</a>, <a href=\"#/G378\">G378</a>, <a href=\"#/G4134\">G4134</a>, <a href=\"#/G4136\">G4136</a>, <a href=\"#/G4137\">G4137</a>, <a href=\"#/G4138\">G4138</a>, <a href=\"#/G466\">G466</a>, <a href=\"#/G4845\">G4845</a>"}]}